      <title>网上经纪公司允许个人投资者购买部分公司债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/public-offers-fractional-trading-of-corporate-bonds-to-retail-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Public Holdings Inc.经纪业务的散户投资者将能够像购买股票一样购买部分公司债券，从而为数万亿美元的固定收益市场带来更广泛的买家基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/public-offers-fractional-trading-of-corporate-bonds-to-retail-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
