      <title>受高利率打击的英国房东正在出售他们的租金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/higher-mortage-rates-push-uk-landlords-to-sell-rentals-even-with-rent-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[更严格的监管和更高的抵押贷款成本迫使许多人缩小规模，导致出租房产更加稀缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/higher-mortage-rates-push-uk-landlords-to-sell-rentals-even-with-rent-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 06:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦两座最昂贵的豪宅正在努力出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/two-of-london-s-most-expensive-mansions-are-struggling-to-sell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦最昂贵的两座豪宅在市场上的总价为 4.75 亿英镑（合 6.02 亿美元），但由于高利率和严峻的税收环境抑制了投资，目前正难以出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/two-of-london-s-most-expensive-mansions-are-struggling-to-sell</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
